<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | GardenRich</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-50 font-sans antialiased text-zinc-900">
    <%- include("partials/header") %>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 mb-4 inline-block">← Back to Home</a>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium mb-12">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 space-y-10">
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">1</span>
                    Information We Collect
                </h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed pl-11">
                    We collect information you provide directly to us when you create an account, make a purchase, or contact support. This includes your name, email address, phone number, and shipping address.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">2</span>
                    How We Use Your Information
                </h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed pl-11">
                    Your data allows us to process orders, send tracking updates, and improve our natural product formulations. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">3</span>
                    Payment Security
                </h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed pl-11">
                    All payments are processed through secure, encrypted gateways. GardenRich does not store your credit card or bank details on our servers.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">4</span>
                    Cookies
                </h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed pl-11">
                    We use cookies to enhance your shopping experience and remember items in your cart. You can disable cookies in your browser settings if preferred.
                </p>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>